main event: A witness observed a bright blue-white object in the sky and captured a photograph of it in late August 1955.
interesting points: The object was observed for a long time before the photograph was taken,The object did not follow a curved path like meteors,The photograph shows unusual colors and a distinct shape,The sighting lasted approximately 15 minutes,The report suggests the object could be evidence of extra-terrestrial visitation.
witness description: the photographer was talking with parents and had a camera ready
